QuestData.Title: Victory!
QuestData.Description: We just can't thank you enough for all that you've done. Now we can all get off of this island before it kills us!$B$BThrall is going to want to speak with you first, $n. I'll rocket you over there.$B$BSee you on the ship!
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Thrall at the Gallywix Docks on the Lost Isles.
